  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT325-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">piriviṭai āṟṟāḷ eṉak kavaṉṟa tōḻikkuk kiḻatti melintu uraittatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Told by HER, when becoming weak, to the confidante, who
          was anxious she would not have the strength in the time of separation. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT325">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> cēṟuñ cēṟu meṉṟaliṟ paṇṭaittaṉ</l>
          <l> māyac celavāc cettu maruṅkaṟṟu</l>
          <l> maṉṉik kaḻikeṉ ṟēṉē yaṉṉō</l>
          <l> vācā kentai yāṇṭuḷaṉ kollō</l>
          <l> karuṅkāl veṇkuruku mēyum</l>
          <l> peruṅkuḷa māyiṟṟeṉ ṉiṭaimulai niṟaintē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l rend="indent2">Earlier when [he] said “we will be going!” ,</l>
          <l rend="indent4">thinking even that his going would be fake,</l>
          <l rend="indent9">I said</l>
          <l>“I shall last [and] pass through [it],</l>
          <l rend="indent6">being torn away from [your] side.” </l>
          <l rend="indent8">Alas!</l>
          <l>Where is he, my father who would be [my] support?</l>
          <l>A big pond, where black-legged white egrets are grazing,</l>
          <l>arose in between my breasts, filling [with tears].</l>

        </lg>
      </div>
